{"tid":1968312,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[程班長事件討論]入面嘅阿斯嘉特fb page相當有可疑 求驗傳媒鞭過","createTime":"2020-04-11T14:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T08:04:12.000Z","uid":148315,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bef2acb50f42263f8bad12817651dd8de60563c7","tid":1968312,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"其中一圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kOLTjkT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkOLTjkT.jpg&h=383766a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳細事件請睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yes158/photos/pcb.1310045369205886/1310759112467845/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyes158%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.1310045369205886%2F1310759112467845%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1WzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=cb4122bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yes158/photos/pcb.1310045369205886/1310759112467845/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n之前有熱狗朋友share阿斯嘉特嘅post<br />\n入咗去個page望一望<br />\n大致內容都係屌泛民同屌非勇武抗爭嗰啲內容<br />\n具體講過咩唔記得<br />\n想入去睇返發現成個page唔見咗<br />\n大家未必判斷到係唔係熱狗<br />\n不過唔緊要 畀大家睇睇佢啲fake news往績先<br />\n(雖然我認同香港人喺外地講普通話係自貶身價)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iOoEZmk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiOoEZmk.jpg&h=9e8a0a64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kauyim/photos/a.701245323285019/2680999831976215/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkauyim%2Fphotos%2Fa.701245323285019%2F2680999831976215%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1WzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=d2a75549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kauyim/photos/a.701245323285019/2680999831976215/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n求驗傳媒 ：<br />\n&quot;左上圖：專頁「阿斯嘉特」質疑日本電視新聞在機場訪問的不是香港人，認為他是內地人假扮香港人。<br />\n<br />\n左下圖：當事人（黃先生）最初在該專頁的澄清，被刪除後只留下cap圖，同時被質疑是否當事人。黃先生表示無法再在該專頁留言。<br />\n<br />\n右上中下：當事人黃先生向本傳媒提供了去日本的機票、當日在機場的相片、近照及香港讀書的證據。<br />\n<br />\n本傳媒確認黃先生是當事人及是一名香港人。<br />\n<br />\n傳送門<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/104630084312904/posts/163519351757310/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F104630084312904%2Fposts%2F163519351757310%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1WzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=42897c2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/104630084312904/posts/163519351757310/?d=n</a><br />\n(已失效)<br />\n&quot;<br />\n<br />\n唔理自稱台灣手足嗰篇嘢係出自邊度<br />\n篇嘢啲語調用詞十分古怪，咩「台灣共和國」<br />\n(大部分台灣人唔認同中華民國甚至想將佢取而代之嘅最多叫「台灣」)<br />\n仲要用中華民國旗就係等於國民黨呢啲嘢都講得出<br />\n擺明係有意分化<br />\n轉發啲咁嘅嘢出嚟係好有問題<br />\n<br />\n其實真係無咁多咩黃絲攻擊同路人嘅case<br />\n大部分都係扮黃搞分化<br />\n等有啲人心理質素頂唔住出嚟呻<br />\n造成黃營眾叛親離嘅樣<br />\n<br />\n程班長向來呻得有啲厭世同偏激<br />\n(例如上次派口罩被屌咁)<br />\n或者有人會懷疑程班長炒作宣傳甚至係同土共網軍同熱狗扯貓尾<br />\n呢啲陰謀論都係不宜鑽落去<br />\n但自稱台灣手足嗰篇嘢同嗰個阿斯嘉特page就肯定有問題<br />\n<br />\n結論：大家要保持心理質素，頂住五毛攻擊，唔好對黃圈同你相信嘅嘢失望<br />\n<br />\np.s.歡迎大家同場討論tg group「阿囝搵老豆老母」嘅做法"},{"pid":"ba150c64bacdf7013a9fd1e151c67fa24492c09a","tid":1968312,"uid":328119,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:50:33.000Z","msg":"可能同HKIP同一類非黑即白既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073590ff38cc59eb7e4f4229e6cea71304ce2ef2","tid":1968312,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:58:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a36486eb15333511c8e245492e2b15f0d60f2ee7","tid":1968312,"uid":65770,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:01:20.000Z","msg":"佢咪藍鳳凰"},{"pid":"7ce145926082c3cc2d79b4ce12d0540b0063cdf0","tid":1968312,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:03:38.000Z","msg":"咪又係個d乜都搵地方入自己友嘅類熱狗page<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4feeb335b142b341a4203efde0cc7b1235cc6f04","tid":1968312,"uid":76382,"like":0,"disli